One of the blue buses belonging to the Bus Rapid Transport scheme in Lagos State has been razed by fire on the Third Mainland Bridge on Wednesday. The Lagos State Traffic Management Agency, via its Twitter handle confirmed that the fire started around 9:30 a.m. The bus which was heading towards Iyana-Oworo caught fire just after Adeniji Adele axis of the bridge. No casualty reported as at the time of filing this report.   